506
00:44:39,300 --> 00:44:40,220
Really?

507
00:44:43,270 --> 00:44:44,680
It wasn't even that hard.

508
00:44:44,770 --> 00:44:46,640
Fine. I'll erase it.

509
00:44:57,320 --> 00:44:58,410
You're right.

510
00:44:59,490 --> 00:45:03,450
I have you to thank, Mr. Park,
for helping a lowlife like me

511
00:45:04,080 --> 00:45:05,620
become an instructor.

512
00:45:06,660 --> 00:45:08,880
