a nice surprise for you

513
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:11,290
as a token of my gratitude.

514
00:45:12,040 --> 00:45:13,130
Please look forward to it.

515
00:45:15,460 --> 00:45:16,800
That's a nice tie.

516
00:45:16,880 --> 00:45:18,050
Is it made of gold foil?

517
00:45:26,930 --> 00:45:29,020
