518
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:30,900
What the heck are you doing?

519
00:45:31,650 --> 00:45:32,860
What was that?

520
00:45:33,230 --> 00:45:34,320
Hey.

521
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:41,490
I was just wondering
if you had wings when you fell.

522
00:45:41,910 --> 00:45:44,910
How does it feel to be number two?

523
00:45:44,990 --> 00:45:45,830
What, you punk?

524
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:48,960
You can't get worked up already.

525
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:52,080
Once my lecture ends,

526
00:45:52,630 --> 00:45:55,590
you're going to get humiliated
in front of the juniors.

